dct_title_s: Bosnia and Herzegovina city graphic 1:15,000. Gorazde. Series M903
dct_description_sm: Alternate title: Gorazde. Transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by 40 meter contour intervals s and spot elevations. "Coordinate conversion WGS-84 to European 1950." This sheet falls within NK 34-1, 1501A, 1:250,000 and 2882II, M709, 1:50,000. "Map informations as of 1993. Compiled in 1995 from best available sources."
